        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protect Our Children's Schools Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education's unobligated COVID-19 funds to be made available to local educational agencies for the purpose of keeping elementary and secondary schools safe.</p>]]>
